OL,3,CCommunity dairy seeks #25,000 to
OL,4,Crestart milk production
OL,6,FSark's only dairy farm is attempting
OL,7,Fto raise #25,000 to purchase a
OL,8,Fpasteuriser, which farmers say is
OL,9,Fcrucial to producing and selling milk
OL,10,Fsafely.
OL,12,FThe dairy has been closed since April
OL,13,Fafter the previous tenants, Jason and
OL,14,FKatherine Salisbury, left after five
OL,15,Fyears, taking their equipment to their
OL,16,FSuffolk farm.
