OL,3,CCommunity dairy seeks #25,000 to
OL,4,Crestart milk production
OL,6,FThe new operators, a couple from
OL,7,FYorkshire, say they need a
OL,8,Fpasteuriser, which protects against
OL,9,Fharmful bacteria in milk, before they
OL,10,Fcan move to the island and safely
OL,11,Fbegin production.
OL,13,FCaragh Couldridge from the Sark
OL,14,FCommunity Dairy Charitable Trust,
OL,15,Fwhich owns the site, says the machine
OL,16,Fwould also enhance the shelf life and
OL,17,Fquality of the milk.
