OL,3,CCommunity dairy seeks #25,000 to
OL,4,Crestart milk production
OL,6,F"For the milk to be available to
OL,7,Feverybody, including the young,
OL,8,Felderly and immunosuppressed, it needs
OL,9,Fto be pasteurised for safety",
OL,10,FKatherine explains, warning that the
OL,11,Fbacteria in raw milk can cause
OL,12,Fdiseases in humans such as
OL,13,Ftuberculosis.
OL,15,F"On a small island, public safety is
OL,16,Feven more important," she adds.
OL,18,FThe Trust hopes to raise #25,000 to
OL,19,Ffund the purchase of a second-hand
OL,20,Fpasteuriser.
