OL,3,CCommunity dairy seeks #25,000 to
OL,4,Crestart milk production
OL,6,FUntil recently, it had planned to buy
OL,7,Fone from Guernsey Dairy, but it is
OL,8,Funderstood that deal fell through.
OL,10,FIn 2017, Sark's dairy farmer retired,
OL,11,Fresulting in the closure of the dairy.
OL,12,FThis meant milk, cream, butter and
OL,13,Fcheese had to be imported from
OL,14,FGuernsey until 2021.
OL,16,FHowever, efforts from the island's
OL,17,Ftight-knit community led to the
OL,18,Fcreation of the Sark Community Dairy
OL,19,FCharitable Trust.
