OL,3,CCommunity dairy seeks #25,000 to
OL,4,Crestart milk production
OL,6,FIt raised almost #500,000 to build a
OL,7,Fcustom facility for the island.
OL,9,FJason and Katherine were selected to
OL,10,Frun the farm following a worldwide
OL,11,Fsearch and moved over in 2019, with
OL,12,Fcows transported to Sark by boat two
OL,13,Fyears later.
OL,15,FNow that they have left, fundraising
OL,16,Fefforts are underway to help the dairy
OL,17,Fproduce pasteurised milk on the island
OL,18,Fonce again.
